OL,3,CNew prisons to be built and offenders'
OL,4,Crecall time reduced, announces Mahmood
OL,6,FShabana Mahmood also announced the
OL,7,Fduration of recall will be limited to
OL,8,F28 days, as she laid out the dire
OL,9,Fstate of the overflowing prisons
OL,10,Fservice with the adult male estate
OL,11,Fcurrently operating at 99% capacity.
OL,13,FThe Ministry of Justice's interim
OL,14,Fpermanent secretary, Amy Rees, said
OL,15,Fthe government would "run out of
OL,16,Fprison places in just five months'
OL,17,Ftime", if further measures were not
OL,18,Ftaken.
