OL,3,CNew prisons to be built and offenders'
OL,4,Crecall time reduced, announces Mahmood
OL,6,F"On our current trajectory, the prison
OL,7,Fpopulation rises by 3,000, and now we
OL,8,Fexpect to hit zero capacity - to
OL,9,Fentirely run out of prison places for
OL,10,Fadult men - in November of this year,"
OL,11,Fthe top civil servant added.
OL,13,FThe latest measures are aimed at
OL,14,Fdealing with the scale of the
OL,15,Fcontinuing crisis in prisons, as the
OL,16,Flatest weekly prison population in
OL,17,FEngland and Wales stands at 88,087.
