OL,4,Crecall time reduced, announces Mahmood
OL,6,FThis is 434 below the last peak in the
OL,7,Fprison population of 88,521 inmates on
OL,8,FSeptember 6. This figure was recorded
OL,9,Fjust before the government began
OL,10,Ffreeing thousands of prisoners early
OL,11,Fas part of efforts to curb jail
OL,12,Fovercrowding - measures which Rees
OL,13,Fsaid were not sufficient and "only
OL,14,Fbought the service time".
