OL,3,CNew prisons to be built and offenders'
OL,4,Crecall time reduced, announces Mahmood
OL,6,FMahmood, speaking at a Downing Street
OL,7,Fpress conference on Wednesday, said
OL,8,Fthe government has agreed funding for
OL,9,Fthree new prisons.
OL,11,FShe confirmed a #4.7 billion package
OL,12,Fof funding would be made available in
OL,13,Fthe spending review to build them -
OL,14,Fbut did not give details on where all
OL,15,Fof the sites would be located.
OL,17,FThese prisons will include "breaking
OL,18,Fground" on a site near HMP Gartree in
OL,19,FLeicestershire "later this year", she
OL,20,Fsaid.
