OL,3,CNew prisons to be built and offenders'
OL,4,Crecall time reduced, announces Mahmood
OL,6,FThe Justice Secretary went on to warn
OL,7,Fthat although the government was
OL,8,Fputting in place "a record prison
OL,9,Fexpansion", it would not be enough to
OL,10,Fsolve the overcrowding.
OL,12,F"Prison building is necessary, but it
OL,13,Fis not sufficient," she said. "We
OL,14,Fcannot build our way out of this
OL,15,Fcrisis."
OL,17,FShe said the plans build on the
OL,18,Fgovernment's pledge to open up 14,000
OL,19,Fprison places by 2031, which she said
OL,20,Fwas "the largest expansion of the
OL,21,Fprison estate since the Victorians".
