OL,3,CNew prisons to be built and offenders'
OL,4,Crecall time reduced, announces Mahmood
OL,6,FOffenders are recalled to prison if
OL,7,Fthey commit another offence when they
OL,8,Fare released early but remain on
OL,9,Flicence.
OL,11,FA standard recall currently results in
OL,12,Foffenders being taken back to prison
OL,13,Ffor the remainder of their sentence,
OL,14,Fbut this can be for shorter fixed-
OL,15,Fterms in some circumstances.
OL,17,FIt is estimated that more than half of
OL,18,Foffenders who are given a sentence of
OL,19,Fless than 12 months go on to re-offend
OL,20,Fupon their release from prison.
