OL,3,CNew prisons to be built and offenders'
OL,4,Crecall time reduced, announces Mahmood
OL,6,FSetting out the measures, she said: "I
OL,7,Fam announcing a measure that will
OL,8,Ftarget the recall population, which
OL,9,Fhas more than doubled in seven years.
OL,11,F"We will bring legislation in the
OL,12,Fcoming weeks that means those serving
OL,13,Fsentences of between one and four
OL,14,Fyears can only be returned to prison
OL,15,Ffor a fixed 28-day period."
OL,17,FShe said some offenders will be
OL,18,Fexcluded from the new measure,
OL,19,Fincluding those who have been recalled
OL,20,Ffor committing another serious offence.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/15
